additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Read safety directions. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone 13 11 26 Australia; 0800 764 766 New Zealand) or a doctor. If swallowed do not induce vomiting. If in eyes, hold eyelids apart and flush the eye continuously with running water. Continue flushing until advised to stop by the Poisons Information Centre or a doctor, or for at least 15 minutes. If skin or hair contact occurs, remove contaminated clothing and flush skin and hair with running water. Corrosive. May produce severe burns. Attacks skin and eyes. Vapour may be harmful.
